---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
import { breadcrumbSchema } from '../utils/seo';

const crumbs = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
  { label: 'Privacy Policy', href: '/privacy-policy' },
];

const effectiveDate = 'January 1, 2025';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How The Herbert Team collects, uses, and protects your personal information, including our use of the Meta Pixel and Google Analytics 4 and how to opt out."
  heroEyebrow="Legal"
  heroTitle="Privacy Policy"
  heroSubtitle={`Effective ${effectiveDate}. This policy explains what we collect, why we collect it, and what control you have over it.`}
  heroImage="/images/hero/contact-hero.jpg"
  heroImageAlt=""
  crumbs={crumbs}
  showHeroCtas={false}
  heroSize="sm"
  schema={breadcrumbSchema(crumbs)}
>
  <Section bg="white">
    <div class="prose mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="lead">
        {site.name} is the mortgage practice of {site.advisor}, {site.nmls}, originating through {site.institution},{' '}
        {site.institutionNmls}. This policy covers information collected through this website. Loan applications
        submitted through the Primis Bank application portal are governed by Primis Bank&rsquo;s own privacy policy and
        Gramm-Leach-Bliley Act privacy notice, which you will receive during the application process.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3>Information you give us</h3>
      <p>When you fill out a form, request a guide, or book a consultation on this site, we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Name, email address, phone number, and mailing or property location</li>
        <li>Details you volunteer about your situation — employment type, purchase timeline, property type, goals</li>
        <li>Message content you send through a contact or partner form</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not collect Social Security numbers, account numbers, or full financial documentation through this
        website. That information is only collected inside the secure Primis Bank application portal.
      </p>

      <h3>Information collected automatically</h3>
      <p>Like nearly every website, ours automatically records technical information when you visit:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>IP address and general geographic region</li>
        <li>Browser type, operating system, and device type</li>
        <li>Pages viewed, time on page, scroll depth, and the link or ad that referred you</li>
        <li>Cookies and similar identifiers set by our analytics and advertising tools</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Advertising and Analytics Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        This website uses two third-party tracking technologies. Both are active on every page, and both set cookies in
        your browser.
      </p>

      <h3>Meta Pixel (Facebook and Instagram)</h3>
      <p>
        We use the Meta Pixel (ID {site.analytics.metaPixel}), a tool provided by Meta Platforms, Inc. It records page
        views and specific actions — such as submitting a form, clicking to call, or starting an application — and sends
        that event data to Meta. We use it to measure which ads produce inquiries and to show relevant ads to people who
        have visited this site. Meta may match this activity to your Facebook or Instagram account if you have one.
      </p>
      <p>
        The pixel does not transmit the contents of your loan file or any financial documentation. It transmits page
        URLs, event names, and browser identifiers.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can control this through
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/adpreferences/ad_settings" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Meta&rsquo;s Ad Preferences</a
        > and
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/help/2207256696182627" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Off-Facebook Activity settings</a
        >, or by opting out through the
        <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Digital Advertising Alliance opt-out page</a
        >.
      </p>

      <h3>Google Analytics 4</h3>
      <p>
        We use Google Analytics 4 (measurement ID {site.analytics.ga4}), a service provided by Google LLC, to understand
        how visitors find and use the site — which pages get read, which guides get downloaded, and where people drop
        off. GA4 collects page views, events, approximate location derived from a truncated IP address, device
        information, and a randomly generated client identifier stored in a cookie.
      </p>
      <p>
        We do not use GA4 to identify you personally, and we do not upload personally identifiable information into
        Google Analytics.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can opt out of Google Analytics on every website you visit by installing the
        <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a
        >, or manage ad personalization at
        <a href="https://myadcenter.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google My Ad Center</a>.
      </p>

      <h3>Other ways to opt out</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Block or delete cookies in your browser settings</li>
        <li>Enable your browser&rsquo;s &ldquo;Do Not Track&rdquo; or Global Privacy Control signal</li>
        <li>Use a private or incognito window, which discards cookies when closed</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Blocking these tools does not affect your ability to use the site, submit a form, or apply for a loan. It only
        limits our measurement.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services We Embed</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Pivot Point CRM</strong> — hosts the contact, partner, guide download, newsletter, and booking forms
          embedded on this site. Information you submit through those forms goes directly to that platform.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Common Ninja</strong> — displays our live Google Reviews widget. It loads review content from Google.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Google Fonts and Google Maps</strong> — deliver typography and the location map. Google may log your IP
          address when these load.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Primis Bank HomeHub</strong> — the secure loan application portal. Once you leave this site for the
          portal, Primis Bank&rsquo;s privacy policy governs.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To respond to your inquiry and provide the mortgage guidance you requested</li>
        <li>To deliver guides, checklists, and other resources you asked for</li>
        <li>To schedule and conduct consultations</li>
        <li>To send occasional educational emails and market updates, which you can unsubscribe from at any time</li>
        <li>To measure marketing performance and improve the website</li>
        <li>To comply with lending, recordkeeping, and advertising regulations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Share Your Information</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>We do not sell your personal information.</strong> We share it only in these situations:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          With {site.institution} and Primis Bank as necessary to process, underwrite, and close your loan
        </li>
        <li>
          With service providers who operate on our behalf — CRM, email delivery, scheduling, and analytics platforms —
          under obligations to protect it
        </li>
        <li>
          With settlement service providers involved in your specific transaction, such as title companies, appraisers,
          and insurance agents
        </li>
        <li>When required by law, subpoena, regulatory examination, or to prevent fraud</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Text Messages and Calls</h2>
      <p>
        By submitting your phone number through a form on this site, you consent to be contacted by phone, text message,
        and email regarding your inquiry, including by automated means. Consent is not a condition of any loan or
        service. Message and data rates may apply. Reply STOP to any text to opt out of text messages, or call
        <a href={site.phoneHref}>{site.phone}</a> to be removed from all contact lists.
      </p>

      <h2>Email Communications</h2>
      <p>
        Every marketing email includes an unsubscribe link. Unsubscribing stops marketing messages but does not stop
        transaction-related communication about a loan already in progress.
      </p>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        This site is served over HTTPS. We use reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect
        information in our possession. No method of transmission over the internet is completely secure, so we cannot
        guarantee absolute security. Please do not email sensitive documents — use the secure portal instead.
      </p>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain inquiry and marketing information for as long as needed to serve you and to meet legal and regulatory
        recordkeeping requirements, which for mortgage-related records is generally a minimum of three years and may be
        longer depending on the record type.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You may request access to the personal information we hold about you, ask us to correct it, or ask us to delete
        it where we are not required to retain it. Residents of states with comprehensive privacy laws may have
        additional rights, including the right to opt out of targeted advertising. To make a request, email
        <a href={site.emailHref}>{site.email}</a> or call <a href={site.phoneHref}>{site.phone}</a>. We may need to
        verify your identity before acting on a request.
      </p>

      <h2>Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This site is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect information from them. If you
        believe a child has submitted information, contact us and we will delete it.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy as our practices or the law change. The effective date at the top reflects the most
        recent revision. Material changes will be posted on this page.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        {site.advisor} &middot; {site.name}<br />
        {site.address}<br />
        <a href={site.phoneHref}>{site.phone}</a><br />
        <a href={site.emailHref}>{site.email}</a>
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm">
        {site.advisor} | {site.nmls} | {site.institution} | {site.institutionNmls} · Equal Housing Lender · Member FDIC
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</PageLayout>
